snippet.title: Amber Heard Pleads No Guilty To Illegal Dog Importation in Australia!
snippet.description:
"Amber Heard was pleading no guilty in illegally sneaking her dogs into Australia, but she knew not that if convicted, she could face 10 years in prison or a $75,000 dollar fine!

Amber Heard is an American actress, who made her film debut in the acclaimed sports drama Friday Night Lights. After small roles in North Country and Alpha Dog, she played her first leading role in All the Boys Love Mandy Lane and appeared in The CW television show Hidden Palms.
